            <h2>
                The Voidreaver
            </h2>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 100;" class="story">
                The Void grows, and the Void adapts—in none of its myriad spawn are these truths more apparent than Kha’Zix. 
                Evolution drives the core of this mutating horror, born to survive and to slay the strong. 
                Where it struggles to do so, it grows new, more effective ways to counter and kill its prey. 
                Initially a mindless beast, Kha’Zix’s intelligence has developed as much as its form. 
                Now, the creature plans out its hunts, and even utilizes the visceral terror it engenders in its victims..
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin-top: 8%; text-align: center; font-size: 25px;filter:drop-shadow(5);" id="buildStory">
                Build your story!
            </h3>
            <input class="inputBox" type="text" name="story" placeholder="What is your name?" style="margin-top: 5%;"
                required="required" id="inputHider">
            <a class="button1" font-size="25" id="disableMe">Away we go!</a>
            <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.0.min.js"></script>
            <script>
                $(".button1").click(function () {
                    const btn = document.getElementById('disableMe');
                    btn.style.display = 'none';
                    const input = document.getElementById('inputHider');
                    input.style.display = 'none';
                    const story = document.getElementById('buildStory');
                    story.style.display = 'none';
                    var name = $(".inputBox").val();
                    
                    if (name.length = 0 || name === undefined || name === null || name === "") {
                        alert("Please enter a name");
                    } else {
                        
                        $(".story").append('<br><br>');
                        var i = 0;
                        var txt = `${name} had always been fascinated by the Void. As a child, he would spend hours staring up at the night sky, wondering what lay beyond the stars. When he grew older, he began to read about the creatures that supposedly lived there, and he became especially interested in one of them: Kha'Zix. He followed every bit of news and lore he could find on the creature, and dreamed of one day meeting it.

And then, one day, his dream came true. ${name} was out on a hike in the woods when he suddenly came across a creature that he knew could only be Kha'Zix. He was terrified, but also excited, and he couldn't help but approach the creature.

Kha'Zix was fascinated by ${name}, and ${name} by Kha'Zix. They talked for hours, about the Void and all the creatures that lived there. ${name} even got to see Kha'Zix hunt, and he was amazed by the creature's intelligence and brutality.

Eventually, ${name} had to go home, but he knew that he would never forget his encounter with Kha'Zix. He had finally found the answers to the questions that had been plaguing him for so long, and he had made a friend in the process.`; /* The text */
                        var speed = 1; /* The speed/duration of the effect in milliseconds */
                        function typeWriter() {
                            if (i < txt.length) {
                                $(".story").append(txt.charAt(i));
                                i++;
                                setTimeout(typeWriter, speed);
                            }
                        }
                        function endingText() {
                            $(".story").append('<br><br>');
                            $(".story").append('<b>This story was generated with GPT3!</b>');
                        }
                        function endingTextTwo() {
                            $(".story").append('<br><br><br>');
                            $(".story").append('<a class="button1" font-size="25" id="enableMe"href="/champions/kalista">Make your story with Kalista, The Spear of Vengence ➤</a>');
                        }

                        typeWriter();
                        setTimeout(endingText, 7000);
                        setTimeout(endingTextTwo, 9000);
                    }
                });
            </script>
